ing%20titles%20in%20unique%20categories%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20putting%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehighlights%2C%C2%A0like%20new%20releases%20or%C2%A0Christmas%20movies%20around%20the%20holidays%2C%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20homepage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwiping%20through%20DraftKings'%20casino%20app%2C%20users%20can%20similarly%20find%20%26quot%3Blobbies%26quot%3B%20with%20carousels%20of%20games.%20They%20include%20the%20top%2010%20slots%20or%20table%20games%2C%20titles%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bonly%20at%20DraftKings%2C%26quot%3B%20recently%20played%20games%2C%20suggested%20games%20for%20a%20particular%20user%2C%20and%20games%20grouped%20by%20themes%20like%20%26quot%3Bspin%20the%20wheel.%26quot%3B%20The%20app%20even%20has%20an%20%26quot%3BEaster%20Hunt%26quot%3B%20section%20right%20now%20with%20spring-themed%20games%20like%20%26quot%3BCharmed%20Rabbits%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BCeltic%20Gold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20really%20modeled%20after%20Netflix%20from%20a%20content%20delivery%20perspective%2C%26quot%3B%20Gottlieb%20said.%20%26quot%3BThis%20next-gen%20lobby%20product%20we've%20created%20essentially%20allows%20our%20operators%20to%20manage%20dozens%20of%20lobbies%20concurrently%20with%20one%20another%2C%20and%20every%20lobby%20is%20themed.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGottlieb%20said%20there%20are%20also%20lobbies%20tailored%20for%20different%20types%20of%20bettors%20like%20VIPs%20and%20casual%20gamers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Netflix%20model%20is%20part%20of%20DraftKings'%20merchandising%20strategy%2C%20one%20of%20three%20pillars%20of%20its%20product%20plan%20that%20also%20includes%20in-house%20content%20and%20gamification.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDraftKings%20has%20doubled%20down%20on%20original%20content%20to%20propel%20its%20casino%20business.%20Gottlieb%20said%20the%20company%20now%20produces%20110%20original%20titles%20through%20its%20casino%20studio%2C%20which%20made%20up%20about%20half%20of%20the%20amount%20wagered%20on%20its%20casino%20games%