rget%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esame-game%20parlays%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20different%20outcomes%20within%20a%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20made%20a%20major%20investment%20both%20in%20bringing%20new%20content%20to%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20%26quot%3Bbringing%20that%20content%20in-house%2C%26quot%3B%20Gottlieb%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20betting%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20this%20gives%20DraftKings%20more%20control%20over%20areas%20like%20pricing%20and%20the%20types%20of%20bets%20it%20offers%2C%20helping%20the%20company%20stand%20out%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20redundant%26quot%3B%20marketplace.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGottlieb%20said%20that%20by%20the%20end%20of%202025%2C%20all%20DraftKings'%20live%20and%20in-game%20betting%20content%20will%20be%20in-house.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20goal%20for%20us%20initially%20was%2C%20how%20do%20we%20just%20sort%20of%20reduce%20a%20third-party%20dependency%2C%20create%20some%20cost%20savings%3F%26quot%3B%20Gottlieb%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20what%20we%20sort%20of%20found%20our%20way%20into%20was%20a%20fully%20functional%20end-to-end%20studio%20with%20everything%20from%20game%20development%20to%20in-house.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdraftkings-models-online-casino-app-netflix-expands-original-games-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742041862000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d4a973b8b41a9673fac5e2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdraftkings-models-online-casino-app-netflix-expands-original-games-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22DraftKings'%20chief%20product%20officer%20explains%20how%20the%20company%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Netflix%20for%20its%20online%20casino%20app%20and%20original%20games%20strategy.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mmeaney%40businessinsider.com%20(Mackenzie%20Meaney)%22%2C%22engageme