OI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fswara-bhasker-shuts-down-trolls-questioning-her-husband-fahad-ahmads-absence-during-holi-celebrations-shares-an-adorable-family-pic%2Farticleshow%2F119044700.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rs%204%2C347%20Crore%20For%20Cricket's%20'Grand%20Slam'.%20Report%20Says%20'Secret%20Plan'%20By...%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESaudi%20Arabia%20is%20planning%20to%20enter%20the%20world%20of%20franchise%20cricket%20by%20injecting%20%24500%20million%20(Rs%C2%A04347%2C42%2C00%2C000)%20into%20a%20T20%20league.%20According%20to%20a%20report%2C%20the%20proposed%20eight-team%20league%20will%20follow%20a%20tennis%20Grand%20Slam-like%20model%2C%20with%20teams%20assembling%20across%20four%20different%20locations%20in%20a%20year.%20The%20league%20will%20be%20backed%20by%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20SRJ%20Sports%20Investments%2C%20headed%20by%20Danny%20Townsend%2C%20a%20former%20chief%20executive%20of%20the%20A-League.%20According%20to%20a%20report%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theage.com.au%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Fgrand-slam-of-cricket-secret-plan-hatched-for-new-saudi-backed-t20-league-20250315-p5ljsr.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Age%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20discussions%20about%20the%20league%20have%20been%20going%20of%20for%20a%20year%20between%20the%C2%A0SRJ%20Sports%20Investments%20and%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20concept%20has%20been%20secretly%20in%20the%20works%20for%20a%20year%20and%20is%20the%20brainchild%20of%20Australian%20Neil%20Maxwell%2C%20the%20former%20NSW%20and%20Victoria%20all-rounder%20who%20manages%20Australian%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Pat%20Cummins%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1656-pat-cummins-playerprofile%5C%22%3EPat%20Cummins%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20is%20a%20former%20board%20member%20of%20the%20Australian%20Cricketers'%20Association%20and%20Cricket%20NSW%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20the%20main%20goal%20of%20this%20project%20is%20to%20address%20the%20sport's%20%26quot%3Bmost%20pressing%20problems%26quot%3B%2C%20including%20the%20growing%20concerns%20over%20the%20sustainability%20of%20Test%20cricket%20beyond%20the%20big%20three%20--%20India%2C%20Australia%20and%20England%20--%20of%20world%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20players%20would%20be%20well%20compensated%2C%20the%20global%20league%20has%20been%20drawn%20up%20aspirationally%20as%20a%20way%20to%20establish%20an%20alternative%20revenue%20source%20beyond%20cricket's%20established%20funding%20model.%20Under%20that%20system%2C%20member%20nations%20receive%20income%20from%20broadcasters%20and%20ICC%20distributions%2C%20but%20it%20is%20weighted%20heavily%20in%20favour%20of%20the%20game's%20superpower%20India%20and%20to%20a%20lesser%20extent%20Australia%20and%20England%2C%20leaving%20small%20countries%20struggling%20for%20financial%20viability%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20league%2C%20if%20approved%20by%20ICC%2C%20would%20be%20played%20in%20vacant%20windows%2C%20without%20disturbing%20the%20calendars%20of%20other%20big%20T20%20tournaments%20like%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL)%20and%20Australia's%20Big%20Bash%20League%20(BBL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20travelling%20league%20would%20complement%2C%20not%20take%20away%20from%2C%20domestic%20T20%20tournaments%20and%20was%20meant%20as%20an%20avenue%20for%20world%20cricket%20to%20address%20growing%20issues%20about%20its%20future.%20Smaller%20nations%20would%20share%20in%20the%20funds%20raised%20and%20it%20is%20hoped%20they%20would%20be%20encouraged%20to%20embrace%20the%20idea%20and%20play%20less%20unprofitable%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20repo