s%20the%20place%20we%20went%20on%20our%20honeymoon%20%E2%80%94%20and%20we'd%20been%20dreaming%20of%20going%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fkelly-ripa-mark-consuelos-vow-renewals-marriage-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Evow%20renewal%3C%2Fa%3E%20ended%20up%20being%20even%20better%20than%20I'd%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22163f890a-de9d-4831-8a7c-c9e3302e1d1e%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAs%20OUTRIGGER%20Reef%20hotel%20guests%2C%20the%20simple%20renewal%20didn't%20cost%20us%20extra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223704%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Hotel%20bed%20with%20bag%20at%20OUTRIGGER%20Reef%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c78642b8b41a9673f9aec5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222785%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20booked%20a%20few%20nights%20at%20OUTRIGGER%20Reef%20Waikiki%20Beach%20Resort%20for%20our%20renewal.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Tibaldi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20researching%20our%20options%20online%2C%20I%20found%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.outrigger.com%2Fhawaii%2Foahu%2Foutrigger-reef-waikiki-beach-resort%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOUTRIGGER%20Reef%20Waikiki%20Beach%20Resort%3C%2Fa%3E%20offered%20a%20vow%20renewal%20free%20of%20charge%20for%20guests%20every%20Tuesday%20and%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20surprised%2C%20as%20other%20hotels%20I'd%20seen%20were%20charging%20hundreds%20of%20dollars%20for%20renewals.%20The%20resort's%20website%20said%20all%20I%20needed%20to%20do%20was%20send%20an%20email%20to%20reserve%20a%20spot%20for%20the%208%20a.m.%20ceremony.%20So%2C%20I%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20place%20on%20a%20nearby%20public%20beach%20area.%20When%20we%20checked%20in%20on%20Sunday%2C%20we%20learned%20we'd%20be%20sharing%20our%20Tuesday%20vow%20renewal%20with%20another%20couple%20at%20the%20resort%20who'd%20also%20signed%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20staff%20member%20at%20the%20reception%20desk%20told%20us%20that%20it's%20tradition%20for%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20to%20present%20each%20other%20with%20a%20flower%20lei%20at%20the%20ceremony%2C%20available%20for%20purchase%20in%20the%20hotel%20lobby%20or%20at%20numerous%20flower%20shops%20in%20the%20neighborhood.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFortunately%2C%20the%20resort%20has%20a%20range%20of%20complimentary%20daily%20programming%20on%20its%20weekly%20activities%20calendar%2C%20and%20one%20event%20was%20a%20lei-making%20class.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20my%20do-it-yourself%20husband%20created%20flower%20garlands%20for%20us%20to%20exchange%20at%20the%20ceremony.%20Our%20room%20had%20a%20mini-fridge%2C%20perfect%20for%20keeping%20the%20blooms%20fresh%20until%20the%20next%20morning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fad40add-7ea4-4a66-a3ca-8ae566d8fb23%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EOur%20vow%20renewal%20on%20the%20beach%20was%20even%20better%20than%20I%20imagined%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223738%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Author%20Allison%20Tibaldi%20and%20her%20husband%20smiling%20with%20a%20person%20in%20red%20on%20the%20beach%20%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c78642b8b41a9673f9aec4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222766%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAlthough%20the%20vow%20renewal%20was%20free%2C%20it%20also%20wasn't%20private.%3Cp%3EAllison%20Tibaldi%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20still%20jet-lagged%20and%20awoke%20early%20Tuesday%20morning%2C%20with%20plenty%20of%20time%20for%20a%20cup%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fa-day-in-the-life-of-the-kona-coffee-cherry--one-of-the-worlds-most-expensive-coffees-2011-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKona%20coffee%3C%2Fa%3E%20before%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sun%20was%20bright%20but%20gentle%20as%20we%20headed%20down%20to%20the%20beautiful%20beach%20in%20front%20of%20the%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20wedding%20organizer%20at%20the%20resort%20greeted%20us%20and%20introduced%20us%20to%20the%20Australian%20couple%20also%20renewing%20their%20vows.%20They%20had%20traveled%20with%20their%20family%2C%20who%20were%20also%20present%20for%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENext%2C%20the%20organizer%20introduced%20us%20to%20the%20officiant%2C%20hula%20dancer%2C%20and%20ukulele%20player%20who'd%20be%20helping%20to%20bring%20our%20ceremony%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20took%20off%20our%20shoes%20and%20walked%20toward%20the%20ocean%20until%20the%20warm%20water%20tickled%20our%20toes.%20Waves%20and%20tropical%20birdsong%20were%20the%20soundtrack%20to%20the%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20officiant%20taught%20us%20how%20to%20do%20the%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-things-growing-up-in-hawaii-maui-local-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHawaiian%20kiss%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20we%20faced%20each%20other%2C%20foreheads%20and%20noses%20touching.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20explained%20that%20placing%20the%20lei%20around%20each%20other's%20necks%20symbolized%20the%20transfer%20of%20love.%20In%20both%20Hawaiian%20and%20English%2C%20he%20said%20a%20few%20short%20vows%20about%20how%20lucky%20we%20were%20to%20be%20in%20love%2C%20and%20we%20repeated%20these%20to%20each%20other%20in%20English.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20and%20I%20placed%20the%20florals%20around%20each%20other's%20necks%20and%20kissed%20Hawaiian-style%20as%20the%20hula%20dancer%20swayed%20and%20the%20ukulele%20player%20serenaded%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d3c6f71-914d-4277-8443-cb88554bd50e%5C%22%3EThe%20experience%20was%20short%20but%20impactful%20%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELastly%2C%20the%20officiant%20handed%20us%20a%20vow-renewal%20certificate%20with%20our%20names%20printed%20on%20it.%20The%20entire%20experience%20was%20over%20by%208%3A45%20a.m.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20professional%20photographer%20took%20photos%20throughout%20the%20ceremony%20that%20were%20available%20for%20purchase%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20feel%20pressured%20to%20buy%20them.%20The%20organizer%20had%20also%20snapped%20images%20of%20us%20during%20the%20ceremony%2C%20as%20did%20the%20family%20of%20the%20Australian%20couple.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeyond%20our%20hotel%20stay%2C%20our%20vow%20renewal%20didn't%20cost%20a%20cent.%20However%2C%20the%20memory%20is%20priceless.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20casual%20ceremony%20felt%20powerful%20and%20intimate%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20we%20were%20on%20a%20public%20beach.%20I%20was%20surprised%20that%20I%20even%20cried.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-vow-renewal-hawaii-resort-outrigger-reef-hotel-review-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742039282000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cf53a2585f1dff88b1b5ab%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-vow-renewal-hawaii-resort-outrigger-reef-hotel-review-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22As%20OUTRIGGER%20Reef%20hotel%20guests%2C%20we%20were%20able%20to%20book%20a%20simple%20vow%20renewal%20ceremony%20on%20a%20beach%20in%20Hawaii%20for%20free%20for%20our%2030th%20wedding%20anniversary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22ehochberg%40businessinsider.com%20(Allison%20Tibaldi)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffree-vow-renewal-hawaii-resort-outrigger-reef-hotel-review-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Inside%20the%20NATO%20team%20prepping%20the%20alliance%20to%20respond%20to%20crisis%20scenarios%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22911%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22US%20forces%20taking%20part%20in%20a%20NATO%20exercise%20in%20March.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d5647eb8b41a9673fac858%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3ESean%20Gallup%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20NATO%20research%20group%20examines%20how%20the%20alliance%20could%20respond%20to%20potential%20crisis%20scenarios.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20provides%20NATO%20leaders%20and%20decision-makers%20with%20analyses%20and%20recommendations.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBI%20spoke%20with%20the%20group's%20director%20about%20her%20team's%20work%20and%20the%20scenario%20she's%20most%20worried%20about.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20NATO%20research%20group%20has%20been%20examining%20some%20of%20the%20most%20potentially%20catastrophic%20scenarios%20facing%20the%20alliance%2C%20including%20a%20possible%20Russian%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20NATO%20Defense%20College%20in%20Rome%20looks%20for%20early%20signs%2C%20dubbed%20%26quot%3Bweak%20signals%2C%26quot%3B%20that%20could%20lead%20to%20significant%20events%20that%20threaten%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20changes%2C%20that%20takes%20a%20different%20direction%20than%20expected%20or%20anticipated%2C%26quot%3B%20Florence%20Gaub%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Research%20Division%20at%20the%20Defense%20College%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20of%20the%20potential%20scenarios%20Gaub's%20team%20is%20studying.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cb34bbd4-5eee-4db9-bd4a-e736ebaf20e2%5C%22%3EStrategic%20foresight%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Research%20Division's%20daily%20work%20includes%20library%20research%2C%20interviews%20with%20NATO%20officers%2C%20brainstorming%20sessions%2C%20and%20scenario%20exercises%20with%20NATO%20and%20member-state%20officials%20to%20identify%20these%20so-called%20weak%20signals%20and%20devise%20potential%20responses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20weak%20signal%20is%2C%20of%20course%2C%20in%20strategic%20foresight%2C%20the%20holy%20grail%20because%20if%20you%20spot%20a%20trend%20very%20early%2C%20you%20buy%20yourself%20a%20lot%20more%20time%20to%20respond%20to%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaub%20said.%20%26quot%3BScenarios%20also%20have%20the%20benefit%20of%20decreasing%20the%20element%20of%20surprise%20and%20reducing%20response%20time.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20work%20has%20become%20increasingly%20important%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20NATO%20has%20faced%20a%20rapidly%20evolving%20security%20environment%2C%20with%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20war%20looming%20on%20its%20eastern%20flank%2C%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20return%20to%20the%20White%20House%20raising%20questions%20over%20the%20US's%20future%20in%20the%20alliance%2C%20and%20China's%20ever-expanding%20global%20influence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGaub%20said%20her%20team's%20current%20areas%20of%20research%20included%20the%20potential%20detonation%20of%20a%20nuclear%20warhead%20in%20space%2C%20panic%20triggered%20by%20speculation%20of%20a%20DNA-gene-editing%20bioweapon%2C%20a%20war%20between%20Egypt%20and%20Ethiopia%20over%20the%20Nile%2C%20Russia%20using%20acoustic%20weapons%20against%20peacekeeping%20forces%20stationed%20in%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20Russia%20testing%20NATO%20with%20a%20missile%20attack%20on%20one%20of%20its%20members%20bordering%20the%20Black%20Sea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20may%20say%20such%20scenarios%20seem%20unlikely%2C%20Gaub%20pointed%20to%20the%20%26quot%3BWhat%20if%20Russia%20and%20China%20became%20allies%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.iss.europa.eu%2Factivities%2Fevent%2Feuiss-munich-security-conference%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Escenario%20exercise%3C%2Fa%3E%20held%20by%20the%20EU%20Institute%20for%20Security%20Studies%20at%20the%202020%20Munich%20Security%20Conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20time%2C%20%26quot%3Ba%20lot%20of%20Europeans%20and%20Americans%20were%20saying%2C%20'That%20will%20never%20happen%2C'%26quot%3B%20Gaub%2C%20who%20previously%20served%20as%20deputy%20director%20at%20the%20EUISS%2C%20said.%20But%20people%20in%20Asia%20and%20Russia%20were%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3B'It's%20already%20happening%2C'%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20years%20later%2C%20Russia%20and%20China%20signed%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-economy-china-no-limits-partnership-yuan-bank-loans-sanctions-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Bno-limits%26quot%3B%20partnership%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Research%20Division%20is%20also%20working%20on%20a%20scenario%20exercise%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%2C%20but%20Gaub%20declined%20to%20provide%20further%20details%20due%20to%20its%20classified%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20of%20the%20division's%20reports%20are%20published%20on%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndc.nato.int%2Fresearch%2Fresearch.php%3Ficode%3D6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20some%20publications%20and%20briefings%20are%20classified%20to%20avoid%20triggering%20%26quot%3Bunnecessary%20drama%26quot%3B%20and%20pushback%20and%20to%20ensure%20that%20Beijing%20and%20Moscow%20do%20not%20have%20easy%20access%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20such%20example%20is%20a%20scenario%20looking%20at%20how%20Russia%20may%20imagine%20a%20nuclear%20war.%20Gaub%20said%20releasing%20a%20report%20on%20this%20subject%20would%20%26quot%3Bunnecessarily%26quot%3B%20scare%20the%20general%20public%20and%20that%20it%20would%20nevertheless%20be%20a%20difficult%20scenario%20to%20write%20on%2C%20given%20that%20the%20only%20historical%20precedents%20%E2%80%94%20the%20atomic%20bombings%20of%20Hiroshima%20and%20Nagasaki%20in%201945%20%E2%80%94%20occurred%20when%20the%20US%20was%20the%20only%20nuclear%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20world%20that%20we%20live%20in%20now%2C%20with%20more%20than%20one%20nuclear%20power%2C%20changes%20the%20game%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaub%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20one%20state%20uses%20a%20nuclear%20weapon%2C%20it%20will%20confront%20the%20situation%20where%20other%20countries%20with%20nuclear%20weapons%20can%20respond.%20That%20makes%20the%20scenarios%20so%20much%20more%20speculative.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2223256c2f-25d5-4462-b2ee-00199a89541a%5C%22%3EThe%20Russian%20threat%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EGaub's%20main%20concern%20at%20present%20is%20that%20a%20Russian%20hybrid%20attack%20on%20a%20NATO%20member%20state%20could%20prompt%20the%20triggering%20of%20the%20alliance's%20Article%205%20%E2%80%94%20which%20stipulates%20that%20an%20armed%20attack%20against%20one%20or%20more%20alliance%20members%20in%20Europe%20or%20North%20America%20shall%20be%20considered%20an%20attack%20against%20them%20all%20%E2%80%94%20but%20that%20allies%20would%20not%20respond.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20is%20suspected%20of%20having%20carried%20out%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-escalating-dangerous-shadow-war-against-nato-could-get-worse-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edozens%20of%20hybrid%20attacks%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20NATO%20in%20recent%20years%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eranging%20from%20arson%20and%20signal%20jamming%20to%20assassination%20attempts%20and%20hacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENo%20member%20state%20has%20so%20far%20triggered%20NATO's%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EArticle%205%20in%20response%20to%20such%20attacks%2C%20which%20Gaub%20said%20were%20%26quot%3Bincreasing%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bbecoming%20more%20and%20more%20aggressive.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20one%20thing%20everybody%20at%20NATO%20is%20afraid%20of%20is%20calling%20the%20day%20on%20Article%205%20and%20discovering%20that%20not%20all%20allies%20are%20on%20board%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESuch%20fears%20may%20have%20been%20heightened%20in%20recent%20months%20as%20Trump%2C%20who%20has%20repeatedly%20criticized%20European%20NATO%20members'%20defense%20spending%2C%20has%20said%20that%20the%20US%20would%20not%20defend%20allies%20who%20didn't%20pay%20enough%20for%20their%20own%20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20effective%20way%20to%20undermine%20NATO's%20cohesion%20is%20to%20engineer%20a%20situation%20that%20is%20%26quot%3Bambiguous%20to%20outsiders%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bclear%20to%20insiders%2C%26quot%3B%20causing%20disagreements%20within%20the%20alliance%2C%20Gaub%20continued.%20%26quot%3BThen%2C%20you%20have%20the%20perfect%20storm.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%20that%20her%20team%20was%20not%20a%20%26quot%3Bprediction%20machine%2C%26quot%3B%20although%20she%20said%20its%20forecasts%20were%20more%20than%2060%25%20accurate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20should%20never%20raise%20the%20expectation%20that%20we're%20going%20to%20be%20accurate%20on%20everything%2C%20especially%20when%20you're%20looking%20at%20black%20swan%20scenarios%2C%26quot%3B%20Gaub%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe're%20in%20the%20business%20of%20low%20probability%2C%20high%20impact%2C%20so%20ideally%2C%20none%20of%20what%20we%20see%20potentially%20happening%20should%20happen.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-nato-team-alliance-crisis-scenarios-russia-military-attack-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742039093000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d56462b8b41a9673fac852%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-nato-team-alliance-crisis-scenarios-russia-military-attack-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20director%20of%20a%20NATO%20research%20group%20told%20BI%20the%20crisis%20scenario%20she's%20most%20worried%20about%20at%20present.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finside-nato-team-alliance-crisis-scenarios-russia-military-attack-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pawan%20Kalyan%20Says%20DMK%20Allows%20Tamil%20Films'%20Dubbing%20In%20Hindi%2C%20Party%20Responds%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20today%20responded%20to%20remarks%20made%20by%20actor-turned-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20over%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ftopic%2Flanguage-row%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eongoing%20language%20debate%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20had%20accused%20Tamil%20Nadu%20politicians%20of%20hypocrisy%2C%20questioning%20why%20they%20opposed%20Hindi%20imposition%20while%20allowing%20Tamil%20films%20to%20be%20dubbed%20into%20Hindi%20for%20commercial%20benefits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDMK%20spokesperson%20Dr%20Syed%20Hafeezullah%20dismissed%20Mr%20Kalyan's%20argument%2C%20calling%20it%20a%20%26quot%3Bhollow%20understanding%26quot%3B%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20stance%20on%20linguistic%20policies.%20%26quot%3BTamil%20Nadu%20has%20never%20opposed%20individuals%20learning%20Hindi%20or%20any%20other%20language.%20What%20we%20oppose%20is%20the%20imposition%20of%20Hindi%20or%20any%20language%20on%20the%20people%20of%20our%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rebuttal%20comes%20amid%20debate%20on%20the%20National%20Education%20Policy%20(NEP)%20and%20the%20Centre's%20push%20for%20Hindi%2C%20which%20Tamil%20Nadu%20has%20historically%20resisted.%20DMK%20leaders%20insist%20that%20equating%20language%20policy%20with%20business%20decisions%20-%20such%20as%20dubbing%20films%20-%20was%20an%20oversimplification%20that%20ignored%20the%20state's%20longstanding%20linguistic%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kalyan%2C%20founder%20of%20the%20Janasena%20Party%2C%20a%20key%20NDA%20ally%20and%20a%20supporter%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20took%20aim%20at%20Tamil%20Nadu%20politicians%20for%20their%20resistance%20to%20Hindi.%20He%20questioned%20why%20Tamil%20Nadu%20leaders%20protested%20against%20Hindi%20while%20Tamil%20films%20continued%20to%20be%20dubbed%20into%20Hindi%20to%20cater%20to%20a%20national%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20do%20not%20understand%20why%20some%20criticise%20Sanskrit.%20Why%20do%20Tamil%20Nadu%20politicians%20oppose%20Hindi%20while%20allowing%20their%20movies%20to%20be%20dubbed%20in%20Hindi%20for%20financial%20gain%3F%20They%20want%20labour%20from%20Bihar%20but%20are%20opposing%20hindi.%20What%20kind%20of%20logic%20is%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Kalyan%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DMK%20responded%20by%20saying%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20already%20has%20Hindi%20Prachar%20Sabhas%20that%20voluntarily%20teach%20Hindi%20to%20those%20interested.%20%26quot%3BIf%20people%20want%20to%20learn%20Hindi%2C%20they%20are%20welcome%20to%20do%20so.%20The%20issue%20arises%20when%20the%20Central%20government%20mandates%20Hindi%20learning%20through%20policies%20like%20the%20NEP%20or%20PM%20SHRI%20schools%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Hafeezullah%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20DMK%20leader%20TKS%20Elangovan%20echoed%20Mr%20Hafeezullah's%20statement%20and%20added%20that%20this%20has%20always%20been%20Tamil%20nadu's%20position%20on%20the%20language%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20been%20opposing%20Hindi%20since%201938.%20We%20had%20passed%20legislation%20in%20the%20state%20assembly%20that%20Tamil%20Nadu%20will%20always%20follow%20the%20two-language%20formula%20because%20of%20the%20advice%20and%20suggestions%20of%20the%20experts%20in%20education%2C%20not%20actors.%20The%20bill%20was%20passed%20way%20back%20in%201968%20when%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20was%20not%20even%20born.%20He%20doesn't%20know%20the%20politics%20of%20Tamil%20Nadu.%20This%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20we%20have%20opposed%20Hindi%20because%20we%20feel%20that%20education%20in%20the%20mother%20tongue%20is%20the%20best%20way%20of%20training%20people.%20He%20(Pawan%20Kalyan)%20wants%20to%20somehow%20support%20the%20BJP%20so%20that%20he%20can%20gain%20something%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%20government%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Elangovan%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EActor-politician%20Prakash%20Raj%20also%20joined%20the%20criticism.%20Taking%20to%20his%20social%20media%20account%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BSomeone%20please%20tell%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20that%20asking%20you%20not%20to%20impose%20your%20language%20on%20us%20is%20not%20hatred%20for%20the%20language%20but%20it%20is%20to%20protect%20our%20language%2C%20our%20mother%2C%20and%20self-respect.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20backed%20Mr%20Kalyan's%20remarks.%20The%20party%20argued%20that%20Hindi%20should%20be%20promoted%20more%20aggressively%20in%20southern%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHindi%20is%20our%20national%20language%2C%20and%20the%20government%20is%20working%20to%20ensure%20it%20reaches%20the%20masses.%20Unfortunately%2C%20previous%20governments%20have%20tried%20to%20suppress%20the%20culture%20of%20nationalism.%20The%20use%20of%20Hindi%20should%20be%20implemented%20strongly%20in%20the%20South%20as%20well%2C%26quot%3B%20BJP%20leader%20Vikram%20Randhawa%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHindi%20is%20one%20of%20the%20official%20languages%20of%20the%20country%20and%20not%20the%20%26quot%3Bnational%20language%26quot%3B%20as%20Mr%20Randhawa%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742039040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fm3qdqp0o_pawan-kalyan-mk-stalin-_625x300_15_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flanguage-row-mk-stalin-pawan-kalyans-tamil-films-dubbed-in-hindi-remark-dmks-actor-jibe-7928066%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Dravida%20Munnetra%20Kazhagam%20(DMK)%20today%20responded%20to%20remarks%20made%20by%20actor-turned-politician%20Pawan%20Kalyan%20over%20the%20ongoing%20language%20debate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Flanguage-row-mk-stalin-pawan-kalyans-tamil-films-dubbed-in-hindi-remark-dmks-actor-jibe-7928066%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22