%2C%20what%20projects%20we%20were%20tackling%2C%20and%20who%20we%20should%20connect%20each%20other%20with.%20But%20over%20time%2C%20it%20evolved%20into%20a%20work-adjacent%20relationship%20that%20is%20part%20mentorship%2C%20part%20friendship%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarting-business-with-partner-strengthened-relationship-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epart%20professional%20partnership%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20calls%20stretch%20beyond%20career%20updates.%20We%20talk%20about%20creative%20pursuits%20%E2%80%94%20me%20writing%20my%20debut%20novel%2C%20Kate%20going%20back%20to%20school%20to%20study%20arboriculture%20(which%2C%20yes%2C%20means%20trees).%20We%20dissect%20our%20personal%20and%20professional%20frustrations%2C%20feeling%20stuck%20or%20burnout.%20We've%20faced%20layoffs%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-rejects-promotions-management-roles-traditional-corporate-ladder-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epromotion%20denials%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20and%20the%20stress%20of%20not%20knowing%20what%20we%20want%20next.%20Through%20it%20all%2C%20Kate%20has%20been%20my%20sounding%20board%2C%20offering%20advice%2C%20encouragement%2C%20and%2C%20most%20importantly%2C%20the%20reminder%20that%20I'm%20not%20alone%20in%20navigating%20work%20and%20life.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnd%20the%20funny%20thing%3F%20We've%20never%20met%20in%20person%2C%20and%20it's%20been%20three%20years.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ffd9de50-c666-4b46-8c87-f76a9ac7cec5%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe've%20kept%20up%20virtually%20so%20far%2C%20but%20our%20friendship%20is%20very%20real%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOur%20friendship%20exists%20entirely%20through%20screens%20and%20texts.%20We%20joke%20about%20it%20often%2C%20how%20strange%20it%20is%20that