%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d4242c69253ccddf994189%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20trains%20to%20use%20the%209K38%20Igla.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFuture%20training%20systems%20will%20be%20only%20in%20virtual%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20PSS%20founder%20Igor%20Belov%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BWe%20do%20it%20right%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20training%20simulators%20offer%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20a%20cheaper%20and%20faster%20training%20process.%20They%20get%20the%20same%20feel%20for%20the%20weapon%20without%20expending%20valuable%20ammunition.%20It's%20also%20a%20safer%20way%20to%20practice%20and%20learn%2C%20as%20Russia%20has%20demonstrated%20that%20it%20will%20launch%20deadly%20strikes%20on%20Ukraine's%20training%20grounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBI%20observed%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20training%20on%20the%20American-made%20.50-caliber%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ukraine-fights-russian-drones-with-truck-mounted-machine-gun-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EM2%20Browning%20machine%20gun%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjavelins-stingers-nlaws-help-ukraine-destroy-russian-tanks-aircraft-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFIM-92%20Stinger%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Soviet-era%209K38%20Igla.%20The%20training%20weapons%20mimic%20the%20real%20deal%20in%20appearance%2C%20weight%2C%20and%20touch%2C%20so%20the%20soldiers%20develop%20strong%20muscle%20memory%20habits%20and%20become%20familiar%20with%20the%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Browning%20is%20a%20popular%20weapon%20for%20Ukrainian%20mobile%20air%20defense%20units%20tasked%20with%20shooting%20down%20Russian%20drones%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-iran-new-drone-may-cause-issues-ukraine-air-defenses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EShahed-136%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Iranian-made%20loitering%20munitions%3B%20Russia%20also%20has%20its%20own%20domestically%20produced%20version.%20The%20heavy%20machine%20guns%20are%20often%20mounted%20in%20the%20beds%20of%20ordinary%20pickup%20trucks.%20The%20Stinger%20and%20Igla%2C%20meanwhile%2C%20are%20man-portable%20air-defense%20systems%2C%20or%20MANPADS.%20These%20shoulder-launched%20weapons%20can%20fire%20missiles%20at%20higher-threat%20targets%20like%20planes%2C%20helicopters%2C%20and%20even%20cruise%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20screen%20shows%20a%20simulated%20combat%20scenario.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d424a8585f1dff88b2263b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20screen%20shows%20a%20simulated%20combat%20scenario.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20soldiers%20wear%20virtual-reality%20goggles%20and%20are%20placed%20in%20simulated%20battlefield%20scenarios.%20An%20operator%20can%20customize%20the%20combat%20experience%2C%20such%20as%20having%20drones%20attack%20from%20different%20directions%20or%20changing%20the%20weather%20to%20a%20low-visibility%20fog%2C%20making%20it%20significantly%20more%20challenging%20to%20spot%20and%20defend%20against%20threats.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIgor%20said%20the%20simulators%20make%20the%20soldiers%20more%20effective%20in%20actual%20combat%20scenarios%2C%20and%20the%20soldiers%20can%20attest%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitaliy%2C%20a%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20in%20an%20anti-aircraft%20unit%2C%20told%20BI%20through%20a%20translator%20that%20there's%20a%20clear%20difference%20between%20the%20simulation%20and%20firing%20a%20real%20gun%20on%20the%20battlefield.%20But%20the%20VR%20experience%20helps%20provide%20that%20muscle%20memory%20and%20feel%20that%20makes%20it%20easier%20to%20use%20the%20weapons%20in%20real%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVitaliy%2C%20who%20is%20identified%20only%20by%20his%20first%20name%20for%20security%20purposes%2C%20said%20training%20on%20the%20Stinger%20is%20easier%20than%20the%20Igla%20because%20the%20American%20launcher%20provides%20its%20operator%20with%20two%20chances%20to%20hit%20a%20target%2C%20whereas%20the%20Soviet%20system%20only%20gives%20one.%20He%20has%20been%20in%20combat%20before%2C%20but%20the%20training%20helps%20him%20keep%20his%20edge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20trains%20to%20use%20the%20M2%20Browning%20machine%20gun.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d424ec69253ccddf994197%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Ukrainian%20soldier%20trains%20to%20use%20the%20M2%20Browning%20machine%20gun.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESoldiers%20serving%20in%20a%20mobile%20air%20defense%20unit%20on%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Kyiv%20told%20BI%20in%20a%20separate%20interview%20that%20simulator%20training%20helped%20them%20hone%20their%20skills%20on%20the%20Browning%20machine%20gun.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20facility%20in%20Kyiv%2C%20this%20reporter%20tested%20the%20Browning%20simulator.%20It%20was%20manageable%20at%20first%20to%20shoot%20down%20a%20few%20slow-moving%20Shahed%20drones%20traveling%20in%20a%20straight%20line%2C%20leading%20the%20airborne%20threats%20by%20aiming%20just%20a%20little%20ahead%20of%20the%20drone%20to%20ensure%20the%20interception%20was%20perfectly%20timed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20as%20more%20drones%20came%20in%20from%20different%20directions%2C%20it%20got%20more%20complicated.%20Eventually%2C%20cruise%20missiles%20were%20added%20into%20the%20mix%2C%20and%20the%20complex%20attack%20became%20completely%20overwhelming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPSS%20offers%20soldiers%20plenty%20of%20other%20weapons%20for%20Ukrainian%20soldiers%20to%20train%20with%20beyond%20air%20defense%2C%20such%20as%20drones%2C%20small%20arms%2C%20or%20anti-tank%20weapons%2C%20like%20the%20Next-generation%20Light%20Anti-tank%20Weapon%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthese-game-changing-weapons-helped-ukraine-spoil-russia-war-plans-2022-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENLAW%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Russian%20Shahed%20drone%20explodes%20during%20a%20simulation.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d4253e585f1dff88b2264c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20Russian%20Shahed%20drone%20explodes%20during%20a%20simulation.%3Cp%3EJake%20Epstein%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20simulator%20service%20is%20offered%20to%20the%20Ukrainian%20military%20at%20no%20cost%20as%20it%20wages%20war%20against%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20force%2C%20but%20Igor%20said%20PSS%20can%20still%20sell%20its%20product%20and%20wants%20to%20put%20it%20on%20the%20international%20market%20for%20foreign%20militaries%20to%20try.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20system%20can%20be%20the%20main%20system%20for%20training%20in%20the%20whole%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Igor%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20necessary%20to%20develop%20as%20fast%20as%20we%20can.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVR%20and%20AR%20training%20is%20a%20highly%20sought-after%20training%20capability.%20Ukraine%20is%20not%20the%20only%20military%20that%20uses%20augmented%20reality%20to%20train%20on%20different%20weapons.%20Last%20year%2C%20this%20reporter%20visited%20a%20facility%20at%20Oklahoma's%20Fort%20Sill%2C%20where%20American%20soldiers%20practice%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fi-tried-downing-enemy-helicopters-us-army-air-defense-simulators-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStinger%20simulators%3C%2Fa%3E%20just%20like%20the%20Ukrainians.%20BI%20has%20also%20prev