%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d4bf1ab8b41a9673fac706%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222371%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERolex%20watches%20showed%20more%20than%2050%25%20in%20returns%20even%20after%20the%20decline%20of%20the%20secondhand%20luxury%20watch%20market%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20a%20study%20showed.%3Cp%3ELeon%20Neal%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20secondhand%20luxury%20watch%20market%20has%20been%20on%20a%20decline%20since%202022.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EStill%2C%20one%20study%20contends%20that%20luxury%20watches%20like%20Rolexes%20have%20less%20volatility.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20study%20also%20found%20that%20high-end%20watches%20saw%20more%20average%20annual%20returns%20than%20real%20estate.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20period%20of%20tariff%20whiplash%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-on-board-ceasefire-trump-must-get-russia-stop-attacks-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egeopolitical%20uncertainty%3C%2Fa%3E%20pushing%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20into%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstock-market-today-sp500-correction-territory-selloff-trump-tariffs-trade-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estock%20market%20correction%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20luxury%20watch%20could%20stand%20the%20test%20of%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20recent%20study%20by%20two%20Swiss%3Cstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3Efinance%20professors%20contends%20that%20luxury%20watches%20saw%20less%20market%20volatility%20than%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Fhousing-market-predictions%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereal%20estate%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20stocks%2C%20and%C2%A0%26quot%3Bfixed%20income%26quot%3B%20or%C2%A0bonds%20when%20examining%20various%20indices%20that%20track%20the%20performance%20of%20those%20assets%20between%C2%A0January%202019%20and%20September%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study's%20findings%20suggested%20that%20high-end%20timepieces%20could%20be%20an%20%26quot%3Battractive%20option%26quot%3B%20for%20investors%20looking%20to%20diversify%20their%20portfolios%20because%20they%20have%20a%20low%20correlation%20with%20the%20stock%20market%2C%20making%20them%20lower-risk%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20watch%20market's%20volatility%20(3.90%25%20annual%20volatility)%20and%20range%20are%20the%20lowest%20of%20any%20asset%20class%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%2C%20which%20was%20published%20February%2024%20on%20Social%20Science%20Research%20Network%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20closest%20asset%20class%20in%20terms%20of%20risk%20is%20fixed%20income%2C%20with%20a%20volatility%20of%205%20to%208%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPhilippe%20Weisskopf%2C%20assistant%20professor%20of%20finance%20who%20co-authored%20the%20paper%20with%20his%20colleague%20at%20EHL%20Hospitality%20Business%20School%2C%20Philippe%20Masset%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview%20that%20one%20caveat%20to%20the%20findings%20is%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-learned-buying-luxury-watches-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eluxury%20watches%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20illiquid%2C%20meaning%20people%20aren't%20selling%20off%20their%20watches%20as%20quickly%20as%20they%20could%20with%20stocks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20not%20that%20many%20transactions%2C%20and%20this%20kind%20of%20artificially%20lowers%20the%20risk%20a%20little%20bit%2C%26quot%3B%20Weisskopf%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20and%20his%20colleague%20tried%20to%20account%20for%20this%20issue%20by%20excluding%20data%20that%20looked%20at%20daily%20price%20movements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReturns%20from%20luxury%20watches%20also%20tell%20a%20mixed%20story.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOverall%2C%20the%20watch%20market%20(5.68%25%20annual%20return)%20underperformed%20equities%20(12.85%25)%20and%20gold%20(13.06%25)%20but%20outperformed%20fixed%20income%20(negative%20returns)%20and%20real%20estate%20(3.14%25)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20brands%2C%20however%2C%20came%20close%20to%20the%20average%20annual%20returns%20seen%20on%20the%20MSCI%20World%20Index%2C%20which%20the%20study%20used%20as%20a%20measure%20of%20global%20stock%20market%20performance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsee-audemars-piguet-ultra-thin-royal-oak-watch-50th-anniversary-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAudemars%20Piguet%3C%2Fa%3E%20showed%2011.68%25%20in%20average%20annual%20returns%2C%20whereas%20stocks%20showed%2012.85%25%20in%20annual%20returns.%20Patek%20Philippe%20showed%20average%20annual%20returns%20of%2010.92%25%2C%20according%20to%20the%20study.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeisskopf%20notes%20that%20brand%20knowledge%20and%20knowledge%20of%20specific%20models%20within%20brands%20are%20crucial%20when%20looking%20into%20luxury%20watch%20investments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ba3d6e30-5d17-4095-9f78-1116d62496dc%5C%22%3EThe%20Rolex%20Recession%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20study's%20conclusion%20factors%20in%20the%20decline%20of%20the%20secondhand%20watch%20market%20in%20the%20past%20three%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20resale%20market%20saw%20a%20huge%20boom%20in%202022%2C%20with%20the%20price%20of%20a%20secondhand%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvestments-in-rolex-watches-beats-houses-gold-dow-jones-average-2022-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERolex%20Daytona%3C%2Fa%3E%20climbing%20to%20its%20peak%20in%20March%20of%20that%20year%20at%20%2448%2C500%20%E2%80%94%20a%20nearly%20228%25%20markup%20from%20its%20retail%20price%20of%20%2414%2C800%20in%202023%2C%20according%20to%20WatchCharts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20the%20estimated%20cost%20of%20a%20resale%20Daytona%20would%20be%20%2427%2C052%20WatchCharts%20data%20showed.%20That%20still%20represents%20about%20an%2083%25%20price%20increase.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeisskopf's%20study%20said%20brands%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolex-ceo-watches-not-investments-dangerous-wrong-message-dufour-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERolex%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Vacheron%20Constantin%20showed%20a%20return%20of%20more%20than%2050%25%20after%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeanwhile%2C%20Audemars%20Piguet%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpatek-philippe-watch-most-expensive-sold-online-auction-christies-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPatek%20Philippe%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20are%20the%20best-performing%20brands%2C%20tripled%20in%20price%20between%202019%20and%202022%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20study%20said.%20%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20the%20two%20brands%20roughly%20doubled%20over%20the%20total%20period%20(i.e.%20from%20January%202019%20to%20September%202024).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWeisskopf%20noted%20during%20the%20interview%20that%20although%20the%20paper's%20findings%20point%20to%20luxury%20watches%20as%20a%20better%20long-term%20investment%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20study%20should%20not%20be%20taken%20as%20investment%20advice.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFrom%20a%20financial%20economist%20point%20of%20view%2C%20I'd%20say%20I%20don't%20see%20how%20the%20watch%20market%20could%20turn%20around%20a%20lot%20right%20now%20if%20you%20look%20at%20what's%20happening%20throughout%20this%20globe%2C%20politically%2C%20geopolitically%2C%20economically%20speaking%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%2C%20right%20now%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20are%20rather%20paying%20a%20bit%20more%20attention%20to%20where%20they%20put%20their%20money.%20So%20I%20don't%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20go%20up.%20Is%20it%20going%20to%20stabilize%3F%20Maybe.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fluxury-watches-rolex-better-investment-than-real-estate-low-volat