%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Arrested%20From%20Aircraft%2C%20Tortured%3A%20Actor%20Ranya%20Rao's%20Explosive%20Allegations%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EActor%20Ranya%20Rao%20has%20claimed%20that%20she%20has%20been%20subjected%20to%20custodial%20torture%20and%20falsely%20implicated%20in%20the%20high-profile%20gold%20smuggling%20case.%20In%20a%20letter%20addressed%20to%20the%20Additional%20Director%20General%20(ADG)%20of%20the%20Directorate%20of%20Revenue%20Intelligence%20(DRI)%2C%20Ms%20Rao%20alleges%20that%20she%20was%20arrested%20directly%20from%20the%20aircraft%20and%20not%20from%20the%20airport%20terminal%2C%20as%20officially%20stated.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20further%20claimed%20she%20was%20physically%20assaulted%2C%20denied%20food%20and%20sleep%2C%20and%20coerced%20into%20signing%20blank%20documents%20under%20duress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20accusations%20come%20a%20day%20after%20a%20special%20court%20in%20Bengaluru%20denied%20her%20bail%20request.%20The%20case%20has%20taken%20a%20political%20turn%2C%20with%20the%20Karnataka%20government%20ordering%20a%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20involvement%20of%20Ms%20Rao's%20stepfather%2C%20Karnataka%20Director%20General%20of%20Police%20K%20Ramachandra%20Rao%2C%20and%20investigating%20possible%20lapses%20by%20law%20enforcement%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Rao%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20DRI%20at%20Kempegowda%20International%20Airport%20on%20March%203%20after%20she%20was%20allegedly%20caught%20smuggling%20over%2014%20kg%20of%20gold%20from%20Dubai.%20However%2C%20in%20her%20letter%20from%20Parappana%20Agrahara%20Central%20Prison%2C%20she%20insists%20she%20was%20detained%20inside%20the%20aircraft%20before%20disembarking%2C%20contradicting%20official%20reports.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%2C%20submitted%20as%20part%20of%20a%20jail%20memo%2C%20contains%20claims%20of%20mistreatment.%20Ms%20Rao%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20slapped%20multiple%20times%2C%20threatened%20with%20exposure%20of%20her%20father's%20identity%2C%20and%20forced%20to%20sign%20blank%20papers.%20She%20alleged%20that%20she%20was%20being%20framed%20to%20shield%20more%20influential%20individuals%20involved%20in%20the%20smuggling%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20these%20allegations%20are%20questionable.%20Ms%20Rao%20wrote%20the%20letter%20on%20March%206.%20She%20was%20brought%20to%20court%20on%20March%209.%20The%20judge%20asked%20her%20three%20times%20whether%20there%20was%20any%20custodial%20torture%2C%20and%20she%20denied%20it%20thrice.%20Neither%20did%20her%20lawyers%20raise%20any%20torture%20allegations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20the%20Special%20Court%20for%20Economic%20Offences%20in%20Bengaluru%20rejected%20Ms%20Rao's%20bail%20plea.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20case%20on%20hand%2C%20the%20accused%20No.1%20(Ranya%20Rao)%20possessing%20Resident%20Identity%20Card%20of%20UAE%20and%20having%20a%20history%20of%20travelled%20to%20Dubai%20on%2027%20occasions%20since%20January%202025%2C%20is%20another%20factor%20which%20does%20not%20incline%20the%20court%20to%20extend%20discretionary%20relief%20of%20granting%20bail%2C%26quot%3B%20%C2%A0Special%20Judge%20Vishwanath%20C%20Gowdar%20observed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20that%20the%20alleged%20offence%20has%20serious%20ramifications%20for%20the%20country's%20economy%2C%20given%20the%20quantity%20of%20gold%20smuggled.%20It%20cited%20preliminary%20findings%20that%20suggest%20Ms%20Rao%20concealed%20gold%20bars%20by%20taping%20them%20to%20her%20body%2C%20placing%20them%20inside%20her%20jeans%20pockets%2C%20and%20even%20hiding%20them%20in%20her%20shoes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20DRI%20has%20estimated%20the%20evasion%20of%20customs%20duties%20and%20penalties%20at%20Rs%204.83%20crore%2C%20far%20exceeding%20the%20legal%20threshold%20of%20Rs%2050%20lakh%20under%20the%20Customs%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20state%20had%20initially%20ordered%20a%20Criminal%20Investigation%20Department%20(CID)%20probe%20into%20protocol%20violations%20at%20the%20airport.%20However%2C%20the%20order%20was%20withdrawn%20within%2024%20hours%2C%20leading%20to%20speculation%20about%20political%20influence.%20Karnataka%20Home%20Minister%20G%20Parameshwara%20defended%20the%20decision%2C%20stating%20that%20since%20the%20Department%20of%20Personnel%20and%20Administrative%20Reforms%20(DPAR)%20was%20already%20handling%20the%20matter%2C%20a%20parallel%20police%20investigation%20was%20unnecessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20a%20complaint%20by%20the%20DRI%2C%20the%20CBI%20has%20launched%20an%20independent%20probe%20into%20the%20alleged%20role%20of%20unknown%20public%20servants%20in%20facilitating%20the%20smuggling%20operation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20March%206%2C%20just%20days%20after%20Ms%20Rao's%20arrest%2C%20two%20foreign%20nationals%20-%20one%20from%20Oman%20and%20another%20from%20the%20UAE%20-%20were%20caught%20smuggling%2021.28%20kg%20of%20gold%20through%20Mumbai's%20Chhatrapati%20Shivaji%20Maharaj%20International%20Airport.%20The%20DRI%20believes%20these%20cases%20are%20interconnected%20and%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20gold%20smuggling%20syndicate%20operating%20from%20Dubai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20possibility%20of%20the%20involvement%20of%20unknown%20public%20servants%20of%20the%20government%20of%20India%20and%20unknown%20others%2C%20with%20such%20coordinated%20network%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20investigated%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20DRI%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFollowing%20Ms%20Rao's%20arrest%2C%20authorities%20conducted%20raids%20at%20her%20residence%2C%20uncovering%20gold%20jewelry%20worth%20Rs%202.06%20crore%20and%20Rs%202.67%20crore%20in%20cash.%20The%20ED%20has%20launched%20a%20money-laundering%20probe%20to%20track%20the%20financial%20transactions%20linked%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742035860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fmkj5624g_ranya-rao-gold-split_625x300_11_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2