%20to%20Paris%20and%20expected%20to%20live%20the%20European%20dream%2C%20but%20the%20reality%20was%20a%20bummer.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20make%20about%20a%20third%20of%20what%20I%20was%20paid%20in%20New%20York%20City%20but%20my%20cost%20of%20living%20hasn't%20changed%20much.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETraveling%20to%20other%20countries%20isn't%20as%20easy%20as%20I'd%20thought%2C%20either.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAbout%20a%20year%20ago%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famerican-in-france-ways-life-has-been-better-changes-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emoved%20to%20Paris%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20living%20in%20New%20York%20City%20for%2010%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20expected%20some%20differences%20%E2%80%94%20mostly%20pleasant.%20I%20imagined%20cheap%2C%20universal%20healthcare%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-work-life-balance-advice-boss-lessons-job-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebetter%20work-life%20balance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20a%20lower%20cost%20of%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20figured%20adapting%20to%20a%20new%20place%20would%20be%20a%20bit%20rough%20initially%2C%20but%20the%20promise%20of%20living%20in%20Paris%20was%20appealing%2C%20and%20leaving%20my%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiktok-staff-burn-out-workplace-performance-pressure-mental-health-leave-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20burnout%3C%2Fa%3E%20seemed%20like%20a%20natural%20transition%20into%20my%20mid-30s.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20reality%20was%20different%20from%20what%20I'd%20imagined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f677bb85-6d27-4b9a-95c2-77bb97999def%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EHealthcare%20in%20Paris%20isn't%20as%20cheap%20as%20I'd%20thought%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20France's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-healthcare-and-insurance-work-around-the-world-2017-7%5C%22%20tar