n%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20pays%20about%20a%20third%20of%20what%20I%20was%20making%20in%20the%20US.%20Yet%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20everyday%20items%20isn't%20significantly%20cheaper.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20pay%20about%20%2480%20a%20week%20in%20groceries%20here%20compared%20to%20%24100%20to%20%24120%20in%20New%20York.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffrench-restaurants-reportedly-requiring-diners-spend-5000-2023-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egoing%20to%20a%20restaurant%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20that%20much%20cheaper%2C%20either.%20In%20New%20York%2C%20I'd%20typically%20pay%20between%20%2425%20to%20%2430%20for%20dinner.%20In%20Paris%2C%20it's%20about%20%2420%20for%20a%20similar%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20services%20are%20even%20more%20expensive.%20I%20spent%20about%20%24300%20in%20New%20York%20to%20color%20my%20hair%2C%20whereas%20it%20costs%20about%20%24350%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20miss%20the%20deals%20I'd%20get%20on%20Amazon.%20Since%20ordering%20on%20Amazon%20in%20Paris%20is%20far%20more%20expensive%20than%20in%20the%20US%2C%20I've%20stopped%20using%20it.%20I%20now%20shop%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20or%20go%20to%20the%20Paris%20equivalent%20of%20Target.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223dfa19c8-ae7f-4a36-8396-042ae00c7ad2%5C%22%3ETraveling%20isn't%20as%20easy%20as%20I'd%20hoped%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20undeniable%20benefit%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fthings-to-know-before-spending-six-months-in-europe-mistakes%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eliving%20in%20Europe%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20ease%20of%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20because%20my%20cost%20of%20living%20is%20almost%20the%20same%20as%20in%20New%20York%2C%20I've%20had%20to%20budget%20more%20for%20travel%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlso%2C%20I'd%20hoped%20that%20planning%20for%20a%20quick%20weekend%20getaway%20in%20Barcelona%20would%20be%20