Cp%3EHe%20started%20two%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investor-shares-his-key-to-generating-cash-flow-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebuild-to-rent%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20projects%20simultaneously%20in%202020%3A%20a%20beach%20house%20in%20Port%20Aransas%20that%20he%20and%20Mindy%20converted%20into%20a%20short-term%20rental%20and%20a%20fourplex%20that%20they%20filled%20with%20long-term%20tenants.%20Both%20projects%20wrapped%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20the%20couple%20expanded%20to%2010%20doors.%20As%20of%20March%202025%2C%20they%20have%20two%20more%20under%20construction%20and%20expect%20to%20have%20a%20total%20of%2012%20completed%20doors%20by%20mid-2025.%20They're%20all%20long-term%20rentals%20except%20the%20beach%20house.%20BI%20viewed%20owner%20statements%20to%20verify%20his%20property%20ownership.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20short-term%20rental%20is%20%26quot%3Bjust%20about%20break%20even%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%2C%20in%20a%20sense%2C%20the%20cash%20flow%20is%20paying%20the%20mortgage%20down.%20And%2C%20it's%20appreciated.%20It's%20doubled%20in%20value.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECash%20flow%20wasn't%20the%20primary%20objective%20of%20this%20project%2C%20he%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIt%20came%20down%20to%2C%20we%20wanted%20to%20have%20a%20beach%20house%2C%20and%20really%20the%20only%20way%20we%20could%20do%20it%20was%20if%20we%20made%20it%20a%20rental%20and%20stayed%20in%20it%20a%20couple%20of%20weeks%20a%20year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20long-term%20rentals%20have%20each%20produced%20positive%20cash%20flow%20from%20the%20get-go%20%E2%80%94%20%26quot%3BI%20wouldn't%20do%20them%20unless%20they%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20%E2%80%94%20and%2C%20as%20of%202025%2C%20are%20profiting%2C%20on%20average%2C%20%24330%20a%20month%20per%20door.%20That's%20about%20%2440%2C000%20a%20year%20of%20relatively%20passive%20income%2C%20as%20his%20properties%20are%20new%20builds%20and%20don't%20require%20much%20maintenance%20or%20attention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20doesn't%20think%20he'd%20get%20close%20to%20those%20numbers%20if%20he%20bought%20pre-existing%20properties%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20resale%20market%20is%20a%20little%20bit%20harder%20to%20pencil%20out%20and%20work%20financially.%26quot%3B%20Plus%2C%20he'll%20be%20able%20to%20pass%20on%20newer%20properties%20to%20his%20family.%20%26quot%3BIf%20I'm%20building%20brand%20new%20and%20I'm%20leaving%20that%20legacy%20for%20the%20family%2C%20by%20the%20time%20I'm%20gone%2C%20these%20properties%20are%20only%2025%20to%2030%20years%20old.%20They're%20still%20in%20great%20condition%2C%20versus%2070-%20or%2080-year-old%20properties%2C%20so%20that's%20another%20factor.%20This%20is%20a%20long-term%20plan%20for%20my%20heirs.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269f7ce20-59f6-43e3-a8ea-a6012ade616b%5C%22%3EInvesting%20in%20real%20estate%20vs.%20the%20stock%20market%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Potts%2C%20who%20set%20a%20lofty%20goal%20and%20was%20working%20with%20a%20relatively%20tight%20timeline%2C%20investing%20in%20real%20estate%20rather%20than%20the%20stock%20market%20made%20more%20sense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20goal%20to%20get%20to%20financial%20freedom%20in%20my%2050s%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20couldn't%20do%20it%20any%20other%20way%20but%20through%20real%20estate%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20do%20this%20well%2C%20it'll%20take%20about%2010%20years.%20You%20can%20get%20to%20financial%20freedom%20much%20quicker%20versus%20using%20a%20401(k)%2C%20which%20is%2030-plus%20years.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225844%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22brannon%20potts%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb4049b8b41a9673fa07d8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224399%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBrannon%20and%20Mindy%20Potts%20reside%20in%20Fort%20Worth%2C%20Texas.%3Cp%3ECourtest%20of%20Brannon%20Potts%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20also%20seeing%20much%20higher%20returns%20than%20he%20would%20if%20his%20money%20was%20in%20a%20fund%20tracking%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%2C%20for%20example.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20wanting%20at%20least%2010%25%20cash-on-cash%20return%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20Once%20he%20finishes%20doors%2011%20and%2012%2C%20%26quot%3Bmy%20average%20cash-on-cash%20return%20is%2027%25.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20expects%20to%20hit%20financial%20independence%20and%20have%20the%20option%20to%20retire%20%E2%80%94%20he%20still%20runs%20his%20property%20management%20company%20%E2%80%94%20once%20he%20gets%20to%2020%20doors%2C%20which%20he%20plans%20to%20do%20in%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20much%20quicker%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BPlus%2C%20the%20asset%20produces%20cash%20flow%20to%20pay%20the%20bills%20so%20you%20don't%20have%20to%20sell%20the%20thing%20that%20you%20own%20as%20equity%20to%20pay%20the%20bills%20%E2%80%94%20it's%20producing%20the%20cash%20flow%2C%20versus%2C%20with%20stocks%20and%20bonds%20and%20a%20401(k)%2C%20you're%20going%20to%20have%20to%20sell%20the%20stock%20to%20create%20the%20cash.%20And%2C%20the%20cash%20flow%20is%20usually%20tax-free.%20The%20IRS%20tax%20code%20is%20written%20for%20owning%20rental%20properties.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20he%20retires%2C%20Potts%20envisions%20himself%20spending%20more%20time%20at%20the%20beach%20and%20with%20his%20kids%20while%20growing%20his%20YouTube%20channel%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40Build2Rent-Investing-Financial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBuild2Rent%20Investing%20and%20Financial%20Talk%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20helping%20others%20use%20real%20estate%20investing%20as%20a%20wealth-building%20tool.%20Part%20of%20the%20reason%20he%20fell%20behind%20on%20retirement%20savings%20in%20the%20first%20place%20was%20a%20lack%20of%20financial%20literacy%2C%20he%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20got%20it%20together%20probably%20in%20my%2040s%2C%20and%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20really%20got%20it%20together%20well%2C%20but%20we%20didn't%20do%20well%20because%20we%20weren't%20taught.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20learned%20the%20importance%20of%20holding%20his%20money%20%26quot%3Baccountable%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20what%20people%20that%20reach%20financial%20freedom%20do.%20If%20you%20treat%20your%20money%20well%2C%20it'll%20come%20back%20with%20friends.%20If%20you%20treat%20your%20money%20poorly%2C%20it'll%20leave%20and%20go%20to%20somebody%20else%20who%20treats%20it%20better.%20So%2C%20I%20want%20to%20treat%20my%20money%20well.%20I%20want%20to%20hold%20it%20accountable%20to%20making%20good%20returns.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-strategy-build-to-rent-cash-financial-freedom-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742033281000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d2f84fb8b41a9673fa8a92%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-strategy-build-to-rent-cash-financial-freedom-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BI%20had%20a%20goal%20to%20get%20to%20financial%20freedom%20in%20my%2050s%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20couldn't%20do%20it%20any%20other%20way%20but%20through%20real%20estate.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22kelkins%40businessinsider.com%20(Kathleen%20Elkins)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freal-estate-investing-strategy-build-to-rent-cash-financial-freedom-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russian%20captain%20of%20ship%20in%20North%20Sea%20crash%20appears%20in%20court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742033280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2