in%20the%20ODI%20format%20have%20made%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20format%20to%20play%26quot%3B%2C%20saying%20that%20the%2050-over-game%20has%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20died%20outside%20of%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%26quot%3B%20due%20to%20batting-friendly%20rules%20of%20powerplay%20and%20two-ball%20rule.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoeen%C2%A0was%20speaking%20to%20Talksport%20Cricket%2C%20as%20quoted%20by%20Wisden.%20Notably%2C%20England%20has%20not%20had%20the%20best%20time%20in%20ODIs%20recently%2C%20having%20massively%20fumbled%20on%20their%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20title%20defence%20in%20India%20back%20in%202023%20with%20just%20three%20wins%20in%20nine%20matches.%20While%20they%20did%20huff%20and%20puff%20their%20way%20to%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20somehow%2C%20they%20finished%20their%20campaign%20recently%20without%20any%20win%20in%20three%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20Talksport%20Cricket%2C%C2%A0Moeen%C2%A0said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20format%20has%20almost%20completely%20died%20out%2C%20apart%20from%20World%20Cups%20and%20Champions%20Trophy.%20It%20is%20the%20worst%20format%20to%20play%20and%20I%20think%20there%20are%20many%20reasons%20for%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoeen%C2%A0said%20that%20the%20rule%20to%20have%20one%20extra%20fielder%20inside%20the%20circle%20(a%20total%20of%20four%20fielders%20outside%20the%2030-yard-circle%2C%20reduction%20from%20five%20earlier%2C%20introduced%20in%202012)%20has%20been%20%26quot%3Bhorrendous%26quot%3B%20as%20it%20is%20not%20easy%20to%20build%20pressure%20on%20batters%20because%20of%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20rules%20are%20terrible.%20To%20have%20that%20extra%20fielder%20in%20after%20the%20first%20powerplay%2C%20I%20think%20it%20is%20a%20horrendous%20rule%20for%20taking%20wickets%2C%20building%20any%20sort%20of%20pressure.%20Guys%20are%20averaging%2060%2C%2070%20in%20ODI%20cricket%20now%20because%20of%20that.%20When%20you're%20bowling%20at%20somebody%20and%20you%20put%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20pressure%2C%20he%20just%20reverse-sweeps%20and%20it%20is%20not%20even%20a%20single%2C%20it%20is%20a%20four.%20It%20is%20just%20there's%20always%20that%20option%20available%20for%20the%20batters%20%5Bto%20score%5D%2C%26quot%3B%20said%C2%A0Moeen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20ANI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742032200000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-02%2Fo8ac3oco_shaheen-afridi_625x300_08_February_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-pacers-are-good-not-the-best-england-world-cup-winners-brutal-verdict-7928821%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Moeen%20Ali%20believes%20that%20the%20current%20Pakistan%20fast%20bowlers%20are%20good%20but%20they%20are%20not%20the%20best%20in%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fpakistan-pacers-are-good-not-the-best-england-world-cup-winners-brutal-verdict-7928821%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20Camera%2C%20Explosive%20Thrown%20At%20Amritsar%20Temple%2C%20Cops%20Hint%20Pak%20ISI%20Links%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20powerful%20explosion%20took%20place%20at%20a%20temple%20in%20Amritsar%20late%20Friday%20night%2C%20shattering%20window%20panes%20and%20damaging%20the%20structure's%20walls.%20CCTV%20footage%20captured%20two%20unidentified%20individuals%20arriving%20on%20a%20motorcycle%20at%20the%20Thakur%20Dwara%20Temple%20in%20the%20Khandwala%20area%2C%20stopping%20briefly%2C%20and%20then%20throwing%20an%20explosive%20towards%20the%20temple%20before%20fleeing.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmritsar%20Police%20Commissioner%20Gurpreet%20Singh%20Bhullar%20confirmed%20that%20the%20police%20were%20alerted%20to%20the%20attack%20at%20approximately%202%20am%20by%20the%20temple's%20priest.%20Senior%20officials%2C%20along%20with%20forensic%20teams%2C%20rushed%20to%20the%20site%20to%20collect%20evidence.%20Commissioner%20Bhullar%20suggested%20a%20possible%20link%20to%20Pakistan's%20Inter-Services%20Intelligence%20(ISI).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20got%20information%20at%202%20am.%20We%20reached%20the%20spot%20right%20away.%20The%20forensic%20team%20was%20called.%20We%20checked%20the%20CCTV%20and%20spoke%20to%20the%20nearby%20people.%20The%20thing%20is%20that%20Pakistan's%20ISI%20lures%20our%20youth%20into%20creating%20disturbances%20in%20Punjab.%20We%20will%20trace%20this%20case%20within%20days%20and%20take%20appropriate%20action.%20I%20warn%20the%20youth%20not%20to%20ruin%20their%20lives.%20We%20will%20catch%20the%20culprits%20soon%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20attack%20has%20triggered%20strong%20political%20reactions%2C%20with%20opposition%20parties%20and%20local%20leaders%20condemning%20the%20deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi-Party-ruled%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20termed%20the%20attack%20a%20%26quot%3Bserious%20and%20sensitive%20incident%26quot%3B%20that%20has%20hurt%20the%20religious%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20SAD%20strongly%20condemned%20the%20incident%20of%20blast%20near%20Thakur%20Duar%20Mandir%20in%20Sri%20Amritsar.%20This%20is%20the%2013th%20such%20blast%20in%20the%20area%20%26amp%3B%20is%20proof%20of%20complete%20collapse%20of%20law%20%26amp%3B%20order%20in%20the%20state.%20It%20is%20a%20serious%20%26amp%3B%20sensitive%20incident%20which%20has%20hurt%20the%20sentiments%20of%20the%20people.%20A%20high%20level%20judicial%20inquiry%20should%20be%20done%20to%20identify%20the%20culprits%20%26amp%3B%20to%20expose%20the%20conspiracy%20behind%20this%20incident%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20party%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SAD%20further%20alleged%20that%20Punjab%20was%20being%20deliberately%20destabilised%2C%20warning%20that%20%26quot%3Bsuch%20experiments%20have%20proved%20dangerous%20in%20the%20past%20and%20are%20once%20again%20pushing%20Punjab%20in%20the%20wrong%20direction.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20Ranveet%20Singh%20Bittu%20also%20criticised%20the%20Punjab%20government%2C%20stating%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20strongly%20condemn%20the%20bomb%20attack%20on%20Thakur%20Dwara%20temple%2C%20Khandwala%20in%20Amritsar.%20AAP%20government%20fails%20to%20check%20repeated%20incidents%20of%20blasts%20in%20border%20city.%20%C2%A0Deteriorating%20law%20and%20order%20in%20Punjab%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20serious%20concern.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20acknowledged%20that%20there%20have%20been%20repeated%20attempts%20to%20disturb%20peace%20in%20the%20state%20but%20maintained%20that%20Punjab's%20law%20and%20order%20remained%20intact%20compared%20to%20other%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20always%20many%20attempts%20to%20disturb%20the%20peace%20in%20Punjab.%20Drugs%2C%20gangsters%2C%20and%20extortion%20are%20part%20of%20it%2C%20and%20there%20are%20attempts%20to%20show%20that%20Punjab%20has%20become%20a%20disturbed%20state.%20During%20the%20festival%20of%20Holi%2C%20in%20other%20states%2C%20the%20police%20had%20to%20use%20a%20lathi%20charge%20during%20processions.%20But%20such%20things%20do%20not%20happen%20in%20Punjab.%20The%20law%20and%20order%20situation%20in%20Punjab%20is%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20investigation%20into%20the%20case%20is%20underway%2C%20police%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742031840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F582jq83g_amritsar-temple-blast-_625x300_15_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Famritsar-temple-blast-on-camera-explosive-thrown-at-amritsar-temple-cops-hint-pak-isi-links-7928709%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20powerful%20explosion%20took%20place%20at%20a%20templ