20comments%20highlighted%20the%20need%20to%20strike%20a%20balance%20between%20reforming%20the%20government%20and%20preserving%20the%20valuable%20work%20done%20by%20its%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMusk's%20approach%20to%20restructuring%20the%20government%20has%20been%20met%20with%20criticism%2C%20particularly%20his%20characterisation%20of%20federal%20workers%20as%20%26quot%3Bfraudsters.%26quot%3B%20Vance%20offered%20a%20more%20nuanced%20perspective%2C%20stating%20that%20while%20some%20individuals%20may%20not%20be%20performing%20their%20duties%20adequately%2C%20it%20is%20essential%20to%20recognise%20the%20valuable%20contributions%20made%20by%20many%20government%20employees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20some%20people%20clearly%20are%20collecting%20a%20check%20and%20not%20doing%20a%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said%20when%20asked%20about%20such%20comments%20from%20Musk.%20%26quot%3BNow%2C%20how%20many%20people%20is%20that%3F%20I%20don't%20know%2C%20in%20a%203%20million-strong%20federal%20workforce%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20few%20thousand%20or%20much%20larger%20than%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance's%20comments%20were%20made%20during%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20aboard%20Air%20Force%20Two%2C%20where%20he%20was%20traveling%20with%20his%20wife%2C%20Usha%20Vance.%20The%20vice%20president%20has%20been%20actively%20engaging%20with%20various%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20visiting%20a%20plastics%20factory%20in%20Bay%20City%2C%20Michigan%2C%20where%20he%20was%20welcomed%20by%20a%20pro-Trump%20audience.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20protesters%20had%20lined%20the%20streets%20leading%20to%20the%20factory%2C%20where%20he%20was%20greeted%20with%20middle%20fingers%2C%20vulgar%20signs%20and%20a%20board%20that%20featured%20a%20crossed-out%20swastika%20which%20read%2C%20%26quot%3BGo%20home%2C%20scumbag%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20previous%20night%20at%20Kennedy%20Center%20in%20Washington%2C%20Vance%20was%20booed%20and%20while%20walking%20his%203-year%20old%20daughter%20in%20Ohio%20last%20weekend%2C%20he%20found%20himself%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20upsetting%20conversation%20with%20Pro-Ukraine%20demonstrators.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20at%20the%20Kennedy%20Center%20I%20thought%20was%20funny%2C%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said%20on%20his%20plane%20Friday%20afternoon.%20%26quot%3BThe%20thing%20by%20my%20house%20I%20thought%20was%20kind%20of%20annoying.%20I%20think%20you%20just%20kind%20of%20take%20the%20good%20with%20the%20bad.%20...%20I%20kind%20of%20just%20see%20it%20as%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20perspective%2C%20a%20feature%20or%20a%20bug%20of%20this%20new%20life.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20remarks%20at%20the%20factory%2C%20Vance%20emphasised%20the%20administration's%20commitment%20to%20manufacturing%20and%20economic%20recovery.%20He%20also%20acknowledged%20the%20challenges%20ahead%2C%20stating%20that%20%26quot%3Bthe%20road%20ahead%20of%20us%20is%20long.%26quot%3B%20Vance%20expressed%20optimism%20about%20the%20progress%20made%20so%20far%2C%20citing%20the%20addition%20of%2010%2C000%20manufacturing%20jobs%20last%20month.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20see%20progress.%20I%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20be%20incremental%20progress.%20But%20I%20also%20think%20it's%20important%20to%20be%20honest%20with%20people%20that%20you%20don't%20get%20to%20%242%20trillion%20deficits%20overnight.%20You're%20not%20going%20to%20get%20out%20of%20%242%20trillion%20deficits%20overnight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20vice%20president's%20comments%20on%20the%20economy%20were%20made%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20growing%20concerns%20about%20the%20impact%20of%20Trump's%20policies.%20Recent%20polls%20have%20shown%20that%20a%20majority%20of%20Americans%20disapprove%20of%20the%20president's%20handling%20of%20the%20economy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E56%25%20of%20adults%20surveyed%20by%20CNN%20and%2054%25%20of%20registered%20voters%20surveyed%20by%20Quinnipiac%20University%20said%20they%20disapproved%20of%20Trump's%20handling%20of%20the%20economy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance%20attributed%20the%20economic%20challenges%20to%20the%20policies%20of%20the%20previous%20administration%2C%20stating%20that%20Trump%20had%20inherited%20a%20difficult%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20discussing%20economic%20issues%2C%20Vance%20also%20shared%20his%20thoughts%20on%20his%20role%20in%20shaping%20the%20administration's%20foreign%20policy%20agenda.%20He%20recalled%20his%20speech%20at%20the%20Munich%20Security%20Conference%2C%20where%20he%20addressed%20issues%20such%20as%20free%20speech%20and%20mass%20migration.%20Vance%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20speaking%20truth%20to%20power%20and%20promoting%20American%20values%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVance's%20comments%20on%20foreign%20policy%20were%20made%20in%20the%20context%20of%20his%20recent%20clash%20with%20Ukrainian%20President%20Volodymyr%20Zelenskyy.%20Vance%20had%20accused%20Zelenskyy%20of%20being%20insufficiently%20thankful%20for%20U.S.%20aid%2C%20sparking%20a%20diplomatic%20row.%20Vance%20acknowledged%20that%20his%20comments%20may%20have%20caused%20controversy%20but%20emphasised%20his%20commitment%20to%20promoting%20American%20interests%20abroad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Vance%20navigates%20the%20complexities%20of%20his%20role%2C%20he%20is%20also%20mindful%20of%20the%20speculation%20surrounding%20his%20potential%20candidacy%20for%20the%20presidency%20in%202028.%20Trump%20had%20raised%20eyebrows%20by%20stating%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Btoo%20early%26quot%3B%20to%20anoint%20Vance%20as%20his%20successor.%20Vance%20brushed%20off%20the%20question%2C%20stating%20that%20he%20is%20focused%20on%20doing%20a%20good%20job%20as%20vice%20president%20rather%20than%20thinking%20about%20his%20future%20political%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20mean%2C%20man%2C%20if%20I%20was%20like%20a%20central%20figure%20to%20getting%20the%20Russia-Ukraine%20crisis%20solved%2C%20who%20gives%20a%20s---%20what%20I%20do%20after%20this%3F%26quot%3B%20Vance%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat's%20kind%20of%20the%20attitude%20I%20take.%20So%20I'm%20very%20focused%20on%20doing%20a%20good%20job.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reflecting%20on%20his%20role%2C%20Vance%20expressed%20a%20sense%20of%20humility%20and%20gratitude.%20%26quot%3BWow%2C%20I'm%20the%20vice%20president-elect%20of%20the%20United%20States%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalled%20thinking%20on%20Election%20Night.%20Vance%20acknowledged%20that%20he%20has%20a%20unique%20opportunity%20to%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20over%20the%20next%20four%20years%20and%20is%20committed%20to%20doing%20so.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742031480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F6e2trbqo_jd-vance-reuters_625x300_15_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-jd-vance-acknowledged-that-elon-musk-made-a-mistake-with-mass-firings-7928759%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Vance%20also%20expressed%20his%20appreciation%20for%20the%20hardworking%20individuals%20within%20the%20federal%20government.%20%26quot%3BThere%20are%20a%20lot%20of%20good%20people%20who%20work%20in%20the%20government%20-%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20doing%20a%20very%20good%20job%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwhen-jd-vance-acknowledged-that-elon-musk-made-a-mistake-with-mass-firings-7928759%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Syrians%20commemorate%20uprising%20anniversary%20for%20first%20time%20since%20Assad's%20fall%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742031135000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-119040432%2Cimgsize-978513.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fsyrians-commemorate-uprising-anniversa