get%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDOGE%3C%2Fa%3E)%2C%20a%20cost-cutting%20initiative%20launched%20under%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20administration.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAs%20DOGE%20faces%20backlash%20over%20layoffs%20and%20budget%20reductions%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20highlighted%20Barack%20Obama's%20remarks%2C%20implying%20that%20Democrats%20once%20endorsed%20similar%20measures.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20seems%20that%20Mr%20Musk%20is%20drawing%20a%20parallel%20between%20DOGE's%20efforts%20and%20the%20former%20president's%20approach%20to%20fiscal%20responsibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20video%20resurfaced%20online%20after%20a%20user%20shared%20it%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter).%20Without%20wasting%20much%20time%2C%20Mr%20Musk%20retweeted%20it%20on%20his%20page%20and%20wrote%2C%20%E2%80%9C%5BBarack%5D%20Obama%20sounds%20exactly%20like%20DOGE!!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EObama%20sounds%20exactly%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDOGE%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40DOGE%3C%2Fa%3E!!%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk92s04pJdY%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fk92s04pJdY%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Elon%20Musk%20(%40elonmusk)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Felonmusk%2Fstatus%2F1900394600394875330%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMarch%2014%2C%202025%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBarack%20Obama's%202011%20%E2%80%98Campaign%20To%20Cut%20Waste'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20video%20shows%20then-president%20Barack%20Obama%20launching%20the%20%E2%80%98Campaign%20To%20Cut%20Waste'%20in%202011%2C%20a%20federal%20initiative%20to%20reduce%20unnecessary%20government%20spending%20and%20tackle%20the%20deficit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIn%20the%20